name: Suspicious Nod-Krai Hot Dog
desc: Classic convenience food. The sausage is too dry, while the bread is too soft, giving the unpleasant impression of chewing on a sponge... If not for hunger, it would be hard not to throw it away...

value.text: Increases all party members' CRIT Rate by 6% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
